### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/health

###
### Add Unit to Favorites
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/favorites
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "your-user-id-here",
  "unitId": "your-unit-id-here"
}

###
### Get User's Favorites
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/favorites/user/your-user-id-here

###
### Check if Unit is Favorited
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/favorites/check/your-unit-id-here/your-user-id-here

###
### Remove Unit from Favorites
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/v1/favorites/your-unit-id-here
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "your-user-id-here"
}
